00:39:20,290 --> 00:39:22,600
   

534
00:39:22,600 --> 00:39:26,510
♫  I really want you  ♫

535
00:39:26,510 --> 00:39:30,890
No, I should take a hint.

536
00:39:30,890 --> 00:39:34,730
♫  I always want to be by your side  ♫

537
00:39:34,730 --> 00:39:39,970
♫  When we spend time together  ♫

538
00:39:39,970 --> 00:39:44,650
Kang Hu Yeong, this isn't right.

539
00:39:44,650 --> 00:39:49,940
It wasn't easy for me to give you up to Hye Ji.

540
00:39:49,940 --> 00:39:54,610
I also had much to tell her today.

541
00:39:56,920 --> 00:40:01,170
♫  I really want you  ♫

542
00:40:01,170 --> 00:40:10,400
♫  I always want to be by your side  ♫

